      "qp4": "Collaboration is key in developing AI in PE/PV further",
      "qp5": "Our datascientists have been to multiple meetings organised by SwissMedic (LLM Task Force workshop on regulatory innovation) where a group could code together and built solutions. That was really great. We would be interested in a range of topics like building a dynamic reporting form usings LLMs to get optimal PV info and immediate FU questions. \n\nAnother topic of interest would be how to evaluate AI tools to make sure that they are regulatory compliant. ",
